title: Headset Radio
description:
Like the track? Click the [↻ Repost] button!

“One of my (Omni) favorite games is 'Jet Set Radio' for the Sega Dreamcast so we thought it would be a good idea to release a kind of tribute to it. In the game, the characters were constantly listening to this really high energy bizarre eclectic music chopped up music on these radio headsets they had so the name is a reference to those. I'd like to think those characters would listen to something like 'Headset Radio'."

title: Super Ubie Land Original Soundtrack - Bonus Boogie (Feelin' Good Mix)
description:
Hey! So, yeah, here's my remix (or, rather, "re-imagining") of the "Bonus Boogie" track from @calumbowen's excellent video game soundtrack "Super Ubie Land Original Soundtrack," which you can purchase here:

http://calumbowen.bandcamp.com/album/super-ubie-land-original-soundtrack

In addition to some fantastic original tunes, check out some sweet remixes by an absolute all-star cast: @skylarspence, @blitzlunar, @aivisura, @hyperduck, and, well, mine's on there too, of course! :)

I had a lot of fun re-working the original material-- I hope you enjoy listening! Let me know what you think! :)
